30
0:01:41.26,000 --> 0:01:43,000
200 million children

31
0:01:43.26,000 --> 0:01:45,000
between four to 14 that

32
0:01:45.26,000 --> 0:01:47,000
should be going to school, but do not;

33
0:01:47.26,000 --> 0:01:49,000
100 million children

34
0:01:49.26,000 --> 0:01:52,000
who go to school but cannot read;

35
0:01:52.26,000 --> 0:01:57,000
125 million who cannot do basic maths.

36
0:01:57.26,000 --> 0:02:02,000
