41
0:02:12.26,000 --> 0:02:15,000
the highest teacher absenteeism

42
0:02:15.26,000 --> 0:02:17,000
in the world,

43
0:02:17.26,000 --> 0:02:19,000
with one out of four teachers

44
0:02:19.26,000 --> 0:02:23,000
