55
0:02:52.26,000 --> 0:02:55,000
and take the child right through school,

56
0:02:55.26,000 --> 0:02:57,000
sent to college,

57
0:02:57.26,000 --> 0:03:01,000
and get them prepared for better living,

58
0:03:01.26,000 --> 0:03:04,000
a high value job."

59
0:03:04.26,000 --> 0:03:07,000
