therapy and mediums of expression.

257
0:13:18.26,000 --> 0:13:21,000
We also believe that

258
0:13:21.26,000 --> 0:13:25,000
it's the content that is more important.

259
0:13:25.26,000 --> 0:13:29,000
It is not the infrastructure,

260
0:13:29.26,000 --> 0:13:32,000
not the toilets, not the libraries,

261
0:13:32.26,000 --> 0:13:35,000
but it is what actually happens in this school

262
0:13:35.26,000 --> 0:13:37,000
that is more important.

263
0:13:37.26,000 --> 0:13:4,000
Creating an environment of learning,

264
0:13:40.26,000 --> 0:13:43,000
of inquiry, of exploration

265
0:13:43.26,000 --> 0:13:45,000
is what is true education.

266
0:13:45.26,000 --> 0:13:47,000
When we started Parikrma

267
0:13:47.26,000 --> 0:13:5,000
we had no idea which direction we were taking.

268
0:13:50.26,000 --> 0:13:53,000
We didn't hire McKinsey to do a business plan.

269
0:13:53.26,000 --> 0:13:56,000
But we know for sure that

270
0:13:56.26,000 --> 0:14:,000
what we want to do today is

271
0:14:00.26,000 --> 0:14:02,000
take one child at a time,

272
0:14:02.26,000 --> 0:14:04,000
not get bogged with numbers,

273
0:14:04.26,000 --> 0:14:08,000
and actually see the child complete

274
0:14:08.26,000 --> 0:14:1,000
the circle of life,

275
0:14:10.26,000 --> 0:14:14,000
and unleash his total potential.

276
0:14:14.26,000 --> 0:14:18,000
We do not believe in scale

277
0:14:18.26,000 --> 0:14:2,000
because we believe in quality,

278
0:14:20.26,000 --> 0:14:24,000
and scale and numbers will automatically happen.

279
0:14:24.26,000 --> 0:14:27,000
We have corporates that have stood behind us,

280
0:14:27.26,000 --> 0:14:3,000
and we are able to, now, open more schools.

281
0:14:30.26,000 --> 0:14:32,000
But we began with the idea

282
0:14:32.26,000 --> 0:14:34,000
of one child at a time.

283
0:14:34.26,000 --> 0:14:37,000
This is five-year-old Parusharam.

284
0:14:37.26,000 --> 0:14:39,000
He was begging

285
0:14:39.26,000 --> 0:14:41,000
by a bus stop a few years ago,

286
0:14:41.26,000 --> 0:14:44,000
got picked up and is now in an orphanage,

287
0:14:44.26,000 --> 0:14:48,000
has been coming to school for the last four and a half months.

288
0:14:48.26,000 --> 0:14:5,000
He's in kindergarten.

289
0:14:50.26,000 --> 0:14:52,000
He has learned how to speak English.

290
0:14:52.26,000 --> 0:14:55,000
We have a model by which kids can speak English

291
0:14:55.26,000 --> 0:14:57,000
and understand English

292
0:14:57.26,000 --> 0:14:59,000
in three month's time.

293
0:14:59.26,000 --> 0:15:02,000
He can tell you stories in English

294
0:15:02.26,000 --> 0:15:04,000
of the thirsty crow, of the crocodile

295
0:15:04.26,000 --> 0:15:06,000
and of the giraffe.

296
0:15:06.26,000 --> 0:15:08,000
And if you ask him what he likes to do

297
0:15:08.26,000 --> 0:15:1,000
he will say, "I like sleeping.

298
0:15:10.26,000 --> 0:15:13,000
I like eating. I like playing."

299
0:15:13.26,000 --> 0:15:15,000
And if you ask him what he wants to do,

300
0:15:15.26,000 --> 0:15:17,000
he will say, "I want to horsing."

301
0:15:17.26,000 --> 0:15:2,000
Now, "horsing" is going for a horse ride.

302
0:15:20.26,000 --> 0:15:23,000
So, Parusharam comes to my office every day.

303
0:15:23.26,000 --> 0:15:26,000
He comes for a tummy rub,

304
0:15:26.26,000 --> 0:15:28,000
because he believes that will give me luck. (Laughter)

305
0:15:28.26,000 --> 0:15:31,000
When I started Parikrma

306
0:15:31.26,000 --> 0:15:35,000
I began with a great deal of arrogance

307
0:15:35.26,000 --> 0:15:37,000
of transforming the world.

308
0:15:37.26,000 --> 0:15:4,000
But today I have been transformed.

309
0:15:40.26,000 --> 0:15:42,000
I have been changed with my children.

310
0:15:42.26,000 --> 0:15:45,000
I've learned so much from them:

311
0:15:45.26,000 --> 0:15:48,000
love, compassion, imagination

312
0:15:48.26,000 --> 0:15:51,000
and such creativity.

313
0:15:51.26,000 --> 0:15:55,000
Parusharam is Parikrma

314
0:15:55.26,000 --> 0:15:58,000
with a simple beginning but a long way to go.

315
0:15:58.26,000 --> 0:16:,000
I promise you, Parusharam

316
0:16:00.26,000 --> 0:16:04,000
will speak in the TED conference a few years from now.

317
0:16:04.26,000 --> 0:16:06,000
Thank you.

318
0:16:06.26,000 --> 0:16:17,000
(Applause)

